	discovery.custhelp.com


	CDN buckets:

		- dsc.discovery.com.edgesuite.net
		- games.dsc.discovery.com.edgesuite.net
		- netstorage.discovery.com.edgesuite.net
		- news.discovery.com.edgesuite.net
